<li>On-going work on <a href="https://github.com/rust-lang/cargo/pull/14058">#14058: <code>cargo:rerun-if-env-changed</code> doesn't work with env configuration</a></li>
<li>On-going work on <a href="https://github.com/rust-lang/cargo/pull/14280">#14280: <code>cargo install --dry-run</code></a></li>
